{
  "stem": "26728.7",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There probably, I don't know, there was a whole row of them, and I had seen-- if I hadn't have known what they were from-- from Buchenwald, I would have had to ask somebody.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "These were four by fours or bigger, and, uh, 10 or 12 feet tall, and they had a rope and a pulley just like a well-- the old-fashioned water well.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they would put this-- these manacles, steel things on the guy's arms, and then hook it onto the chain and just pull him on up there.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I've got some pictures of that, too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I just-- it's-- and let them hang there till they died.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Talk about crucifixion being bad.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It couldn't have been this bad.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Probably three days.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now I'm going to say something, and I hope this-- I'm going to use the F word, and I didn't say this.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When we left, this-- there was a colonel that I had flown-- that had flown in with somebody else and was going to fly back with me, and I don't even remember why.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, um, I had pre-flighted the airplane and everything was ready to go.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we-- we say, he says let's have another-- one more smoke.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we're standing there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we had to get away from the airplane because of the-- the fuel, the gasoline.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we were just standing 5, 10 feet away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he was telling me some other stuff that he had found out that I didn't know about by-- by going around with these other guys.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And some of the stuff they were-- and had to write a report, uh, to, uh, General Eisenhower and so on.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he was just furious.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
